result.name: Mrs Tang Cafe

reviews.text: Awesome breakfast here. Pineapple bun, fried egg and tomato slice. Absolutely delicious. I dont want to know calorie count, but its worth it. The wait can be long if its busy, so go early or during off peak times. The milk tea is good too, so get the whole experience and order it.
Great place great food. Small store easy to pass by if you are traveling this place is a must try. Food is really good here except service to be really fast it's at the center of industrial zone.
Great Hong Kong Style mill tea and noodles soup, long waiting all the day but worth waiting....

Offering local food but seating and hygiene a bit messy.
Seating are crowded and not comfortable.
Kitchen door was wide opened and we saw kitchen staff pouring wasted food on floor and the sewage almost threw to the service floor. 
Not really recommended to visit given there are so many other local cafe in Kwun tong.
A very traditional Hong Kong style cafe! The milk tea is very good and I will recommend that!

result.name: 華嫂冰室

reviews.text: 好食❗
食物一般啦，同其他茶記無乜分別，有啲名過於實。同屏山老店相比，就係少咗份鄉村嘅氣息，所以咪比下去囉。
43元豬排米粉加一杯凍O柚子蜜。吾算貴。豬排美道吾錯吾硬幾好味。食粉、麫加12元有杯野飲。低過食飽要散叫。
